      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.eOrFkkHvGjHFLqFC]{Immortal Tutor (Su) - Aeon}</p>\n<p>When you cast a 1st-level or higher technomancer spell, you can gain the tutor’s first lesson for a number of rounds equal to your Intelligence modifier. After you do so, you can’t use the first lesson again until you have rested 10 minutes to regain Stamina Points.</p>\n<p><strong>First Lesson:</strong> When you make an attack that would deal a damage type you have not dealt since the beginning of your last turn, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to the attack roll.</p>"
